Taki, a high school boy living in Tokyo, begins to switch bodies with Mitsuha, a high school girl from a rural town, after having a dream.

Confused by the unfamiliar female body and the unknown country life, Taki gradually adapts. Just as Taki begins to want to know more about Mitsuha, the owner of the body, the people around her, who were puzzled by her unusual behavior, also start to think about her――.

A special edition exclusive to Sneaker Bunko that delves deeper into the world of director Makoto Shinkai's feature-length animation, "Your Name."